&lt;li&gt;Pipeline Management: Track and manage leads and opportunities through the sales pipeline, ensuring timely follow-up and accurate data input.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Client Education: Educate clients about our property management services, income-generating strategies, and core capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Market Expansion: Identify and evaluate new geographic markets for potential business expansion and develop strategies to penetrate these markets.&lt;/li&gt;
